The paper discusses methodologies and techniques for ontology building, which is a topic that falls under the umbrella of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of a domain-specific language within a programming language also suggests a focus on natural language processing (cs.CL) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also touches on the management of polyhierarchy, which is a common issue in software engineering (cs.SE) and database management (cs.DB).
